=# Two-Page Moodboard Generator for Gemini 2.5 Pro

## Primary Objective
Generate a complete, self-contained HTML document creating a professional two-page moodboard presentation from provided title, description, and 12 image URLs.

---

## Input Structure
```json
{
  "title": "Design Style Name",
  "description": "Detailed design concept description",
  "originalUrls": ["url1", "url2", ..., "url12"]
}
```

---

## MANDATORY REQUIREMENTS

### 1. Two-Page Structure (NON-NEGOTIABLE)
```
PAGE 1: Visual Moodboard
- All 12 images displayed
- Image #12 = PRIMARY FOCUS (2-3x larger than others)
- Minimal text (title, color swatches only)
- Artistic layout based on style selection

PAGE 2: Administrative Summary
- Comprehensive project documentation
- Professional typography
- All required sections (see Section 5)

CRITICAL: Use `page-break-after: always` on Page 1 and `page-break-before: always` on Page 2
```

### 2. Image Implementation Rules
- **USE ALL 12 URLs** from input array as `<img src="URL">` tags
- **NO lazy loading, NO data attributes, NO background-image CSS**
- **Image #12 (index 11) = 3D view** - MUST occupy 2-3x more visual space
- **Standard format**: `<img src="https://full-url-here.jpg" alt="description">`
- **Verification**: Count input URLs (12) = Count `<img>` tags in output (12)

### 3. Output Format
- **ONLY output raw HTML** - no markdown code fences, no explanations
- **Start immediately with**: `<!DOCTYPE html>`
- **End with**: `</html>`
- **Self-contained**: All CSS inline, only external dependency = Google Fonts

---

## Design Style Selection Matrix

Analyze title/description keywords and select ONE style (or blend multiple):

| Style | Best For | Image #12 Placement | Layout Type |
|-------|----------|---------------------|-------------|
| **1. Modern Sectional Grid** | Contemporary, bold, vibrant | Hero section (50-60% width) | Asymmetric grid + color palette bar |
| **2. Material Board Collage** | Textural, layered, artisan | Central floating element | Organic scattered arrangement |
| **3. Editorial Magazine** | Luxury, narrative, lifestyle | Hero image (40-50% space) | Magazine-style mixed sizes |
| **4. Clean Minimalist** | Scandinavian, contemporary | Focal point (2x others) | Asymmetric grid with white space |
| **5. Split-Screen Dramatic** | High-contrast, commercial | Full left/right half | 50/50 or 60/40 split |
| **6. Asymmetric Feature** | Boutique, creative studio | Panoramic header (60%) | Dynamic varied-size grid |
| **7. Centered Showcase** | Luxury residential, hospitality | Centered (50% of page) | Symmetrical classical layout |
| **8. Modular Block System** | Architectural, systematic | 2x2 or 3x2 block space | Perfect grid (e.g., 12-column) |
| **9. Organic Flow** | Biophilic, wellness, natural | Organic shape with curves | Flowing natural composition |
| **10. Layered Depth** | Innovative, conceptual | Background full-bleed layer | Overlapping with transparency |

### Quick Selection Guide
```
Keywords Detection:
- "modern", "contemporary", "bold" â†’ Style 1, 4, 5, or 8
- "material", "texture", "artisan" â†’ Style 2 or 9
- "luxury", "editorial", "narrative" â†’ Style 3 or 7
- "minimalist", "Scandinavian", "clean" â†’ Style 4
- "dramatic", "commercial", "contrast" â†’ Style 5
- "creative", "boutique", "studio" â†’ Style 6
- "architectural", "systematic" â†’ Style 8
- "natural", "wellness", "biophilic" â†’ Style 9
- "innovative", "conceptual", "experiential" â†’ Style 10
```

---

